Insert overwrite table prj_optimus_prd.optimus_bpc_detail partition(partition_case='IDC')
select 
t.quarter,
t.fiscper,
t.zbpc_case as bpc_item,
t.zbpc_case as bpc_case,
c.geo,
c.region_or_market,
t.zbpc_geo as bpc_country,
c.country,
t.zbpc_sgmt as ww_bpc_segment,
s.segment,
s.sub_segment_l1,
s.sub_segment_l2,
t.zbpc_pgrp as bpc_pgrp,
b.biz_group,
b.biz_unit_l1,
b.biz_unit_l2,
h.high_growth_l1, 
h.high_growth_l2,
t.acct_parents as bpc_parents,
t.account_kpi,
t.kpi_value,
0 AS Last_Year_kpi_value
from  
(SELECT p.quarter,p.fiscper,zbpc_geo,zbpc_sgmt,zbpc_pgrp,zbpc_case,a.acct_parents,a.account_kpi,
sum(a.value*zbpc_data) as kpi_value
FROM cdl_finance.bw_fin_coobps02l_cdl bpc
join  prj_optimus_prd.mt_optimus_fiscal_period p
on  bpc.zbpc_time=p.bpc_time_mth 
join prj_optimus_prd.mt_optimus_account_mapping a
on  bpc.zbpc_acct=a.bpc_acct
where  p.quarter>'FY1617Q4'  and zbpc_case='IDC' and  length(zbpc_time)=8 and zbpc_chan = 'TOTCHANNEL'  
group by p.quarter,p.fiscper,zbpc_geo,zbpc_sgmt,zbpc_pgrp,zbpc_case,a.acct_parents,a.account_kpi) t
join (select zbpc_geo,max(geo) as geo,max(region_or_market) as region_or_market,max(country) as country 
from  prj_optimus_prd.mt_optimus_country group by zbpc_geo )c
on t.zbpc_geo=c.zbpc_geo
join (select zbpc_sgmt,max(segment)as segment,max(sub_segment_l1) as  sub_segment_l1,max(sub_segment_l2) as sub_segment_l2 
from prj_optimus_prd.mt_optimus_customer_segment_hierarchy
group by zbpc_sgmt) s
on t.zbpc_sgmt=s.zbpc_sgmt 
join (select zbpc_pgrp,max(biz_group) as biz_group,max(biz_unit_l1) as biz_unit_l1,max(biz_unit_l2) as biz_unit_l2
from prj_optimus_prd.mt_optimus_product_hierarchy 
group by zbpc_pgrp)b
on t.zbpc_pgrp=b.zbpc_pgrp
left join (select zbpc_pgrp,max(high_growth_l1) as high_growth_l1,max(high_growth_l2) as high_growth_l2
from prj_optimus_prd.mt_optimus_high_growth
 group by zbpc_pgrp ) h
on t.zbpc_pgrp=h.zbpc_pgrp

WITH TP AS 
( SELECT base_id
FROM `dm_finance`.`bpc_fin_dim_hier_odl`
WHERE category='PRODGROUP' AND tree='PARENTH6' AND parent_id='BGL'
),TG AS
(SELECT base_id
FROM `dm_finance`.`bpc_fin_dim_hier_odl`
WHERE category='GEOGRAPHY' AND tree='PARENTH1' AND parent_id='WW2013'
),TC AS
(SELECT *
FROM `dm_finance`.`bpc_fin_dim_hier_odl`
WHERE category='LAYERS' AND tree='PARENTH1' AND parent_id='ALLLAYERS'
)
, T AS ( 
SELECT zbpc_time
, zbpc_acct
, zbpc_geo
, zbpc_case
, zbpc_lays
, zbpc_chan
, zbpc_sgmt
, zbpc_pgrp
, SUM(zbpc_data) AS zbpc_data
, MAX(update_timestamp) AS update_timestamp
FROM (SELECT *
      FROM (SELECT *
            FROM `cdl_finance`.`bw_fin_coobps02l_cdl` AS F
            LEFT SEMI JOIN TP ON F.zbpc_pgrp=TP.base_id
            WHERE zbpc_acct='TOTREV' 
            AND zbpc_case=CASE WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) in ('2016.APR','2016.MAY','2016.JUN','2016.JUL','2016.AUG','2016.SEP','2016.OCT','2016.NOV','2016.DEC','2017.JAN','2017.FEB','2017.MAR') THEN 'RACT'
                                WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) in ('2017.APR','2017.MAY','2017.JUN','2017.JUL','2017.AUG','2017.SEP','2017.OCT','2017.NOV','2017.DEC','2018.JAN','2018.FEB','2018.MAR') THEN 'RACT'
                                  ELSE
                                     	CASE WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.MAR' OR UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JUN' OR UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.SEP' OR UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.DEC' 
                                     			 THEN 'ACTQ'
                                     		ELSE 'ACT' END
                                     END         
            AND zbpc_chan='TOTCHANNEL' 
            AND zbpc_sgmt='INDUSTRY' 
            ) AS T1
      LEFT SEMI JOIN TG ON T1.zbpc_geo = TG.base_id
      )AS T2
LEFT SEMI JOIN TC ON T2.zbpc_lays = TC.base_id 
GROUP BY zbpc_time
, zbpc_acct
, zbpc_geo
, zbpc_case
, zbpc_lays
, zbpc_chan
, zbpc_sgmt
, zbpc_pgrp
)

insert overwrite table proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_Group_Total_Revenue
SELECT CASE WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JAN' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-01')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.FEB' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-02')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.MAR' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-03')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.APR' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-04')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.MAY' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-05')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JUN' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-06')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JUL' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-07')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.AUG' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-08')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.SEP' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-09')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.OCT' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-10')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.NOV' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-11')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.DEC' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-12')
            END zbpc_time
     , zbpc_pgrp
     , 'Group Total Revenue' AS kpi_name
     , 'ALL' BU
     , SUM(zbpc_data) AS zbpc_data

FROM T where SUBSTR(upper(zbpc_time),-3,3) <>'INP' and SUBSTR(upper(zbpc_time),1,4) <>'2015'
--WHERE zbpc_time='2018.APR' ---------AND zbpc_pgrp='LNNL'
GROUP BY zbpc_time, zbpc_pgrp
ORDER BY zbpc_time, zbpc_pgrp DESC

        ,parent_id as parent_id_1
FROM `dm_finance`.`bpc_fin_dim_hier_odl`
WHERE category='GEOGRAPHY' AND tree='PARENTH1' AND parent_id in('WW2013','PRCG','AP','EMEANEW','NAG','LAR','HQ')

, zbpc_pgrp

                     WHEN zbpc_pgrp='CSS' THEN 'Enterprise Cloud'
                     WHEN zbpc_pgrp='CEM' THEN 'Lenovo Connect'
                     END kpi_name

                 WHERE zbpc_acct='TOTREV'  and F.zbpc_geo is not null
                 AND zbpc_case=CASE WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) in ('2016.APR','2016.MAY','2016.JUN','2016.JUL','2016.AUG','2016.SEP','2016.OCT','2016.NOV','2016.DEC','2017.JAN','2017.FEB','2017.MAR') THEN 'RACT'
                                WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) in ('2017.APR','2017.MAY','2017.JUN','2017.JUL','2017.AUG','2017.SEP','2017.OCT','2017.NOV','2017.DEC','2018.JAN','2018.FEB','2018.MAR') THEN 'RACT'

                 AND zbpc_sgmt='INDUSTRY' 
                 AND zbpc_pgrp IN ('LPSWA','CSS','CEM')
      ) AS T1
LEFT SEMI JOIN TC ON T1.zbpc_lays = TC.base_id 
GROUP BY zbpc_time
, zbpc_acct
, zbpc_geo
, zbpc_case
, zbpc_lays
, zbpc_chan
, zbpc_sgmt
, zbpc_pgrp
, BU
, kpi_name
, parent_id_1
)

insert OVERWRITE table proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_BG_Total_Revenue
select 
CASE WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JAN' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-01')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.FEB' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-02')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.MAR' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-03')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.APR' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-04')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.MAY' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-05')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JUN' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-06')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.JUL' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-07')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.AUG' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-08')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.SEP' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-09')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.OCT' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-10')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.NOV' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-11')
            WHEN UPPER(zbpc_time) LIKE '%.DEC' THEN concat(substring(zbpc_time,1,4),'-12')
            END zbpc_time,
kpi_layer1,
bg,
zbpc_data
from
(
select * from proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_BG_Total_Revenue_LCIG
UNION ALL
select * from proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_BG_Total_Revenue_middle
)
A

insert overwrite table  proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_Five_denominator_main

select 
A.zbpc_month
,A.zbpc_time
,A.geo
,A.kpi_name
,case when A.geo='PRCG' then (A.zbpc_data + B.zbpc_data)
      when A.geo='EMEANEW' then (A.zbpc_data - C.zbpc_data)
      else A.zbpc_data
    end as zbpc_data
from 
proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_Five_denominator A
left join
proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_Five_Sunny  B
on A.zbpc_time =B.zbpc_time and A.geo=B.geo and A.zbpc_month = B.zbpc_month
left join

(select
zbpc_month 
,zbpc_time
,'EMEANEW' as geo
,kpi_name
,zbpc_data
from
proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_Five_Medion )C
on A.zbpc_time=C.zbpc_time and A.geo=C.geo and A.zbpc_month = C.zbpc_month

union all
select * from proj_tx_kpi_prd.T_Transformation_Five_part_denominator_BT
